'''Bounty hunter armor''' was a form of [[Armor/Legends|armor]] that was often seen being used by [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunters]] throughout [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]].

A popular model of armor known as the [[Bounty Hunter Armor]] was in use during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]]. However, it was not primary used by bounty hunters but by [[Spacer/Legends|spacers]] and criminals.<ref name="SWG">{{GalaxiesAED}}</ref>

